<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../includes/head.ejs') %>
    <style>
        .about-page { position: relative; background-color: #f0fdfa; overflow-x: hidden; }
        .about-background { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 150%; height: 250px; border-top-left-radius: 50%; border-top-right-radius: 50%; background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #0d9488, #22d3ee); z-index: 1; }
        .about-content { position: relative; z-index: 10; }
        .text-teal { color: #0d9488; }
        .quote-section { background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #2dd4bf, #22d3ee); color: white; border-radius: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .team-card {
            background-color: white; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border: 2px solid #a7f3d0; width: 90%; max-width: 320px; 
            margin: auto; transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .team-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .team-card img {
            width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%; border: 4px solid #5eead4;
            object-fit: contain; background-color: #f1f5f9;
        }
        .instagram-section { background-color: white; border-radius: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        .btn-instagram { background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #0d9488, #22d3ee); color: white; font-weight: 600; border: none; }
        .carousel-item { transition: transform .6s ease-in-out; }
        .carousel-item img { border-radius: 1.5rem; }
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            #teamCarousel .carousel-control-prev,
            #teamCarousel .carousel-control-next { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/navbar-landing.ejs') %>

    <div class="about-page">
        <div class="about-background"></div>
        <div class="container about-content py-5">
            <section class="text-center py-5 my-5 wow fadeIn">
                <h1 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-teal">About TBCare</h1>
                <p class="lead text-secondary mt-3 mx-auto" style="max-width: 800px;">Project ini didanai oleh <b>Belmawa - Dikti - Kemendiktisaintek RI</b> dan digarap oleh tim <b>PKM-KC Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember</b>.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="my-5 py-5">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0 wow fadeInLeft">
                        <h3 class="h2 font-weight-bold text-teal mb-4">Sistem Peringatan Dini Tuberkulosis Berdasarkan Suara Batuk</h3>
                        <p class="text-secondary" style="font-size: 1.1rem;"><b>TBCare</b> adalah sebuah sistem inovatif...<br><br>Misi TBCare adalah... menciptakan masa depan Indonesia yang lebih sehat.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInRight">
                        <div id="imageCarousel" class="carousel slide shadow-lg" data-ride="carousel">
                            <div class="carousel-inner">
                                <div class="carousel-item active"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/berita1.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Berita 1"></div>
                                <div class="carousel-item"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/berita2.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Berita 2"></div>
                                <div class="carousel-item"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/berita3.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Berita 3"></div>
                                <div class="carousel-item"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/berita4.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Berita 4"></div>
                            </div>
                            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#imageCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev"><span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span></a>
                            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#imageCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next"><span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="my-5 py-5 wow fadeInUp">
                 <div class="quote-section p-5 text-center">
                    <h3 class="h2 font-weight-light">“Teknologi hadir bukan hanya untuk mempermudah, tapi juga untuk menyelamatkan nyawa. Bersama TBCare, mari wujudkan Indonesia bebas Tuberkulosis 2030.”</h3>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="my-5 py-5 text-center wow fadeIn">
                <h2 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-teal mb-5">Our Team</h2>
                <div id="teamCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4"><div class="team-card p-4"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/nathania.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Nathania"><h4 class="mt-3">Nathania</h4><p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">Project Manager</p></div></div>
                                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 d-none d-md-block"><div class="team-card p-4"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/smiski.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Miskiyah"><h4 class="mt-3">Miskiyah</h4><p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">Website & Design</p></div></div>
                                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 d-none d-md-block"><div class="team-card p-4"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/faisal.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Faisal"><h4 class="mt-3">Faisal</h4><p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">AI & Data</p></div></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4"><div class="team-card p-4"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/rizki.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Rizki"><h4 class="mt-3">Rizki</h4><p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">Mobile App</p></div></div>
                                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 d-none d-md-block"><div class="team-card p-4"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/stanis.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Stanis"><h4 class="mt-3">Stanis</h4><p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">Hardware & IoT</p></div></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#teamCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev" style="width: auto; left: -50px;"><span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" style="background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border-radius: 50%; padding: 20px;"></span></a>
                    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#teamCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next" style="width: auto; right: -50px;"><span class="carousel-control-next-icon" style="background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border-radius: 50%; padding: 20px;"></span></a>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="my-5 py-5 wow fadeInUp">
                <div class="instagram-section p-5">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-left mb-4 mb-md-0"><h3 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-warning">Ikuti Perjalanan Kami!</h3><p class="text-secondary my-4">Dapatkan informasi terbaru mengenai perkembangan TBCare, riset, dan berita seputar teknologi kesehatan langsung dari kami.</p><a href="https://instagram.com/tbcare.its" target="_blank" class="btn btn-instagram rounded-pill px-5 py-3">Follow us on Instagram</a></div>
                        <div class="col-md-6"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/ig.png" alt="Instagram Preview" class="img-fluid rounded shadow"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/footer-landing.ejs') %>
    <%- include('../includes/end.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>